# Foundry Licensing

This repository contains components under different licenses:

## @foundry/primitives — MIT License

The core primitives (agents, adapters, providers, and shared utilities) are
licensed under the MIT License. See [LICENSE-MIT](./LICENSE-MIT) for the full
text.

**Scope:** `src/agents/`, `src/adapters/`, `src/providers/`, `src/logger/`,
`src/db/`, `src/index.ts`

## Foundry (Harness) — Business Source License 1.1

The Foundry harness, orchestration, viewer, and tooling are licensed under the
Business Source License 1.1. You may use, copy, and modify this code freely for
any purpose **except** production commercial use. The BSL automatically converts
to MIT on the Change Date.

See [LICENSE-BSL](./LICENSE-BSL) for the full text.

**Scope:** `src/setup.ts`, `src/start.ts`, `src/demo.ts`, `src/viewer/`

## Foundry Oracle — Proprietary

The Oracle scoring service is proprietary and will be distributed separately
under commercial terms. It is not included in this repository.
